title: Iron Maiden - The Reincarnation of Benjamin Breeg [Single] [320k
description:
"The Reincarnation of Benjamin Breeg" is a song by Iron Maiden from their 14th studio album, A Matter of Life and Death. The song is the leading single from the album, released on 14 August 2006.

The CD single comes with a B-side of "Hallowed Be Thy Name" from the BBC Radio 1 Legends Session. Due to the overall length of the two songs, the single was not eligible for chart inclusion in the UK. The guitar solo in "The Reincarnation of Benjamin Breeg" is played by Dave Murray.
